msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212649_94420da907d0e6e84558b49bf526dfe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212649_94420da907d0e6e84558b49bf526dfe5.jpg&h=35713b87&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n800萬先中</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  邊有得咁計 ！ 就係你咁撚貪心 ，永遠無你份</blockquote><br />\n六合彩有8億咁多咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 安已畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你讀港大呢數位都未撚識睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068711c95a1e6d7844f46819676d7a16334fdf78","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左中頭獎.<br />\n中二獎, 小既幾十萬, 多既二百幾萬. 睇下彩數. <br />\n中三獎, 最多咪十幾萬, 點會改善到生活</blockquote>中三獎可能真係當多左零用<br />\n二獎就可以有d改變 可能做想做既野"},{"pid":"15ec2b1ec2a60fad631bab887144ca73cc003aea","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身都識佢 但係佢宜家唔識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢後唔認人？"},{"pid":"a7fb5c4cf79b174ef05cc7a2b21494a8718f2d90","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老豆fd中咗頭獎<br />\n果期兩個人中都分到7千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩七千萬<br />\n佢生活有咩野變化<br />\n性格會唔會唔同左</blockquote><br />\n工照開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得最fd果堆知佢做咗有錢佬<br />\n使錢好撚豪氣</blockquote><br />\n其實有ff過中頭獎後 都係會做而家既工作<br />\n因為當初係自己決定揀呢份工 亦做得開心<br />\n但或者會少d返工"},{"pid":"6a579264e6a3ed818136b586903fa03383776ca7","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中過3獎<br />\n8萬幾<br />\n交晒學費</blockquote><br />\n都叫做幫輕左 本身可能交學費筆負擔好大"},{"pid":"972e0e399ee0663ad338508deec8caf6881a9bcd","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個fd中過一次三獎 8萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無記錯係13年晚暑期金多寶個期<br />\n<br />\n生活無任何變化 只係多左d錢洗<br />\n<br />\n同成日同我地班fd講點解唔中埋最後一個字 個期頭獎成幾千萬<br />\n<br />\nbtw 佢一買係買4條 5期咁買 <br />\n<br />\n中完呢期 之後個期中左兩條40蚊<br />\n<br />\n兩條各中三個字 仲要全部唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間接頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半杯水哲學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有八萬幾零用都幾好<br />\n可以手鬆d咁買下想買既野"},{"pid":"8531473688b4c7efd5a64d8649670b7d257c5a1f","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企中過幾次3獎 <br />\n得幾萬蚊 食餐好就無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都好呀 每次一中就去食餐好 買下野咁"},{"pid":"4b664b34d0dcb78c105207cb5dd6a8c9fc902334","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友中過3獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己中親都係40雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n仲要10期10期買單式"},{"pid":"616dac976b57e33f421d427996bf4ca6a88e75fc","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得幾萬 冇咩特別<br />\n隔離屋頭獎，但係收埋左十幾年先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係冇咩特別</blockquote><br />\n你果度風水幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔離屋中頭獎但係咪打風流工<br />\n覺得中左到時可以做d唔受氣既工"},{"pid":"324219264a6fee6285a555976bdfefcd6df8d281","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中過，買左架私人飛機返工就唔洗同人逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你吹水定響外國中"},{"pid":"4db229e825328c8acdc2561df151386909ab6e94","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中2，3獎可以改變到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能可以投資開間店？"},{"pid":"f790c33cd8d31016168dadefe859ddfd766104ef","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆fd中過 二千幾萬 買咗三棟樓分俾佢啲仔女</blockquote><br />\n嘩好爽 佢地d仔女無啦啦一人一棟"},{"pid":"2d68a11ff987eb5d723f783fa836f0d56ada3483","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/212649_94420da907d0e6e84558b49bf526dfe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F212649_94420da907d0e6e84558b49bf526dfe5.jpg&h=35713b87&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你點樣用呢筆錢"},{"pid":"7e4d178c89836fb4fd90e490ce2ffc1efb60a703","tid":412173,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"<bl