期買2注<br />\n每期都中廿蚊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cbf687e3a959b859172a99bbe06bc681df9d24","tid":412173,"uid":90872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:24:37.000Z","msg":"老豆朋友中過2定3獎<br />\n用黎投資<br />\n過幾年都係破左產"},{"pid":"b98108e2e85ab8f1ec51c85faf5c6050651a79ea","tid":412173,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"買電腦飛中過3獎<br />\n幾日用哂"},{"pid":"d26865960c20f5e3386d9f9de1e3b15a735f8fc7","tid":412173,"uid":71217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"朋友個游水教練中咗七千萬"},{"pid":"d6d546c7adbe3936fea2ca731962dc8fb98fd72b","tid":412173,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屋企人中過三萬蚊<br />\n好快洗晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三萬蚊可能真係用黎食下野去下旅行已經用完 但都開心</blockquote><br />\n旅行都冇去<br />\n交下學費 唔知做左啲咩就用左一大截<br />\n點知問返另一個差唔多年紀一齊中既男仔女仔<br />\n佢地冇用過<br />\n就好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係你地夾份買一齊share返？<br />\n點解後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊夾份買 咪除返開<br />\n<br />\n後悔冇儲起<br />\n又唔係洗左落咩特別野度 去多幾次旅行都話有啲回憶<br />\n宜家諗起都唔知做左咩<br />\n宜家好努力想儲返嗰筆錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4dbe02deb21769810e7e4967a159e7cb347cde","tid":412173,"uid":33022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三獎 爭一個字就中哂<br />\n佢出10 我買左20 <br />\n得9萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，所有中三獎嘅人都係差一個字中頭獎架啦"},{"pid":"ea693a6b052bcd42d840ec9629badca9f0d7d46d","tid":412173,"uid":33022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最多中過四個半字<img 